<p class="small-margin-before">The exclusive Head tennis racket with the autograph of Robin Söderling – Swedish pro tennis player, No. 4 in ATP ranking. Goes with a set of tennis balls, set of over grips, three packs of tennis strings, a cap and a bag.<br>Robin’s career highlights include reaching two consecutive Grand Slam finals at the French Open in 2009 and 2010, and an ATP World Tour Masters 1000 title at the 2010 Paris Masters.<br>In 2014-2015 Robin Söderling took the role of Tournament Director at Stockholm Open.<br>In 2017 Robin Söderling joined TokenStars in the role of advisor and will help to develop the tennis stream of the platform.</p>
